query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS saudi_economic_indicators (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  indicator_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  month INT NOT NULL,
  year INT NOT NULL,
  quarter INT,
  indicator_code VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  indicator_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  indicator_name_ar VARCHAR(255),
  category ENUM('gdp', 'employment', 'inflation', 'trade', 'monetary', 'fiscal', 'demographics', 'other') NOT NULL,
  value INT NOT NULL,
  unit VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  display_value VARCHAR(100),
  previous_value INT,
  change_from_previous INT,
  percentage_change INT,
  data_source VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  source_url VARCHAR(500),
  reliability ENUM('official', 'estimated', 'provisional') DEFAULT 'official',
  notes TEXT,
  fetched_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX idx_indicator_code (indicator_code),
  INDEX idx_category (category),
  INDEX idx_date (year, month)
);
